episodes.title: Episode 95 - Sarah Hightower: Cults
episodes.description: Lizzie and Kaveh talk about their election angst and interview anti-cult activist and researcher Sarah Hightower. We discuss the Japanese death cult Aum Shinrikyo as well as Q-ANON.Send your questions and comments to hopquestions@gmail.com, or leave a voicemail at 408-444-6623 Hosted on Acast.
